metadata.name: Old City Walls
metadata.description:
Abstract assemblage art, manipulated digitally, created with recycled material. This chaos of colorful patterns layered with icons of my generations sub culture.Petrol based products, these plastics, shaping human nature as well as the nature it self and resembling a lucid vision of  flooding river with fluorescent colors. 

The stencils on work, made from Asena Hayal's portraits, a brave inspiring women who is organizing street art festivals and enable opportunities for young artists in the market.
